text: George Innocent (13 May 1885 - 4 April 1957) was a British swimmer. He competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics and the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1885 births Category:1957 deaths Category:British male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Great Britain Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Swimmers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from London
